# TC-031 – Verify ZIP Code rejects letters-only and special characters input

## 🧪 Test Steps
1. Open Add New Address form
2. Enter a valid country name
3. Enter a valid name
4. Enter a valid mobile phone number
5. Enter an alphanumeric value in the ZIP Code field (e.g., A1B2C3 or 123ABC)   
6. Fill all other required fields  
7. Click on "Submit"

---

## ✅ Expected Result
- Letters-only input is rejected  
- Special characters are rejected  
- Validation message is displayed (e.g., "Invalid ZIP Code format")  
- Field is highlighted in red  
- Form is not submitted  
